text: Psydrax suborbicularis is a species of flowering plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Papua New Guinea. ==External links== *World Checklist of Rubiaceae * World Conservation Monitoring Centre 1998. Canthium suborbiculare. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.
